NAME
    NUKE - Remove "ABC.S" artifact

SYNOPSIS
    NUKE

DESCRIPTION
    Removes a specific file named "ABC.S" (containing quotes
    and a non-printable DEL character) that is sometimes
    created during Krusader assembler testing.

    This command is useful because the filename cannot be
    easily typed at the standard command prompt.

SEE ALSO
    RM, DEL
